            <paragraph classes="classref-method" ids="class-curve2d-method-get-point-in" names="class_curve2d_method_get_point_in"><reference internal="True" refuri="class_vector2#class-vector2"><inline classes="std std-ref">Vector2</inline></reference> <strong>get_point_in</strong> <strong>(</strong> <reference internal="True" refuri="class_int#class-int"><inline classes="std std-ref">int</inline></reference> idx <strong>)</strong> <abbreviation explanation="本方法没有副作用。不会修改该实例的任何成员变量。">const</abbreviation></paragraph>
            <paragraph>返回指向顶点 <literal>idx</literal> 的控制点的位置。返回的位置是相对于顶点 <literal>idx</literal> 的。如果索引越界，则该函数将向控制台发送一个错误，并返回 <literal>(0, 0)</literal>。</paragraph>
            <transition classes="classref-item-separator"></transition>
            <target refid="class-curve2d-method-get-point-out"></target>
            <paragraph classes="classref-method" ids="class-curve2d-method-get-point-out" names="class_curve2d_method_get_point_out"><reference internal="True" refuri="class_vector2#class-vector2"><inline classes="std std-ref">Vector2</inline></reference> <strong>get_point_out</strong> <strong>(</strong> <reference internal="True" refuri="class_int#class-int"><inline classes="std std-ref">int</inline></reference> idx <strong>)</strong> <abbreviation explanation="本方法没有副作用。不会修改该实例的任何成员变量。">const</abbreviation></paragraph>
            <paragraph>返回离向顶点 <literal>idx</literal> 的控制点的位置。返回的位置是相对于顶点 <literal>idx</literal> 的。如果索引越界，则该函数将向控制台发送一个错误，并返回 <literal>(0, 0)</literal>。</paragraph>
            <transition classes="classref-item-separator"></transition>
            <target refid="class-curve2d-method-get-point-position"></target>
            <paragraph classes="classref-method" ids="class-curve2d-method-get-point-position" names="class_curve2d_method_get_point_position"><reference internal="True" refuri="class_vector2#class-vector2"><inline classes="std std-ref">Vector2</inline></reference> <strong>get_point_position</strong> <strong>(</strong> <reference internal="True" refuri="class_int#class-int"><inline classes="std std-ref">int</inline></reference> idx <strong>)</strong> <abbreviation explanation="本方法没有副作用。不会修改该实例的任何成员变量。">const</abbreviation></paragraph>
            <paragraph>返回顶点的位置 <literal>idx</literal>。如果索引越界，则该函数将向控制台发送一个错误，并返回 <literal>(0, 0)</literal>。</paragraph>
