            <paragraph classes="classref-method" ids="class-curve2d-method-samplef" names="class_curve2d_method_samplef"><reference internal="True" refuri="class_vector2#class-vector2"><inline classes="std std-ref">Vector2</inline></reference> <strong>samplef</strong> <strong>(</strong> <reference internal="True" refuri="class_float#class-float"><inline classes="std std-ref">float</inline></reference> fofs <strong>)</strong> <abbreviation explanation="本方法没有副作用。不会修改该实例的任何成员变量。">const</abbreviation></paragraph>
